<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Polar Bear Cloak Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Retrieve a Polar Bear Skin from a Polar Bear.  They are a rare drop so you may need to try many times.<BR>
<BR>
2) Give the Polar Bear Skin and 5pp to Karg Icebear (He wanders the Everfrost Zone) and you will receive a Polar Bear Cloak.</div>
<BR>
