<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I don't know if DE's are KOS to Karg Icebear.<BR>
<BR>
What I do know is that Karg is very hard to come by, here's why.<BR>
<BR>
Although Karg is a good source for a low lvl magical cloak, the polar bear cloak, he is also the guy you have to kill to get Martar Icebear to spawn.<BR>
<BR>
By killing Martar, you will receive a much nicer Cloak of the Ice Bear.<BR>
<BR>
Be careful, Martar is a high lvl baddy. He has killed me on numberous ocasions. I am a barbarian and not KOS to Karg, but all are KOS to Martar.<BR>
<BR>
